PageResultInfo

public PageResultInfo(String pageToken,
                      boolean isFirstPage,
                      boolean isLastPage)
Constructs a new PageResultInfo.

Parameters:
pageToken - A String that locates the current page of results within the complete result set. The token can be used in the PageInfo parameter of further requests for results.
isFirstPage - true if the current page of results is the first page; false otherwise.
isLastPage - true if the current page of results is the last page; false otherwise.
